-(Emily shrieks)

01:26.387 --> 01:28.156
Hallelujah.

01:28.189 --> 01:29.923
(whoops)

01:29.957 --> 01:32.160
Looks like
we got some fresh protein.

01:32.193 --> 01:33.994
-Won't they be contaminated?
-No.

01:34.027 --> 01:35.229
We'll scan 'em.

01:35.263 --> 01:38.098
I don't see any mutations.

01:38.132 --> 01:40.134
Boy, this looks
like good eating, huh?

01:40.168 --> 01:42.136
(Mead whoops)

01:42.170 --> 01:44.272
