out there.

21:39.165 --> 21:42.669
On the way here,
I came across a woman.

21:42.702 --> 21:45.472
A young mother
with two children.

21:45.505 --> 21:47.374
They were some
of the unlucky ones

21:47.407 --> 21:49.576
