22:00.219 --> 22:02.021
Sores.

22:02.054 --> 22:05.425
Their lungs were burnt
from the toxic air.

22:07.360 --> 22:09.796
After a few moments, I realized

22:09.829 --> 22:12.131
that the child she was carrying
in her arms

22:12.164 --> 22:15.034
was already dead.

22:15.067 --> 22:16.969
She was begging for us

22:17.003 --> 22:19.472
to murder her other child
out of pity.

22:19.506 --> 22:21.140
Mercy.

22:21.173 --> 22:24.411
She didn't have the strength
to do it herself,

22:24.444 --> 22:27.480
